&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;Male Acute, Male PICU and Male Autistic Spectrum Disorder (ASD)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary:&lt;/strong&gt;£30,205 per annum (including enhancements)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours:&lt;/strong&gt; Up to 38.5 per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cygnet Hospital Wyke&lt;/strong&gt; is transforming. Committed to delivering safe, effective, person-centred care, we are looking to recruit &lt;strong&gt;Preceptorship (RMN/RNLD) &lt;/strong&gt;Nurses who share our ambition to be outstanding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start your career with us and you’ll have access to a highly-structured quality preceptorship programme. Supported by an experienced preceptor and our Practice Development Nurse, we’ll develop your confidence and skills to become an independent professional. Our programme includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive induction and orientation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Individual/group clinical supervision and reflective practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical skills sessions e.g. assessing and managing clinical risks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leadership training e.g. managing a shift, dealing with conflict&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal wellbeing and building resilience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with local universities, we are building a culture of clinical excellence with opportunities to undertake research in practice and evaluate latest evidence based interventions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Cygnet? We’ll offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS and employee discount scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50% NMC registration renewal paid by Cygnet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free meals on duty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RCNi membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company paid Life Assurance schemeSmart Health Toolkit- Providing you with Fitness Programmes, Nutrition consultation and Health checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
